description:
This is a 365 minute workout called 'The running vibes you need ' from the channel cassie.selfe.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no one’s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
